    public interface DebugVC50TypeLeafIndices

    Enumerates the leaf indices referenced in type strings contained in the DebugVC50SSGlobalTypes subsection. (Some of the descriptions are taken directly from Microsoft's documentation and are copyrighted by Microsoft.)

    NOTE that these indices are specified as integers rather than short integers; this is to make comparisons and switches simpler because of Java's automatic sign extension.
